2-3-74 showed how one essence, one real world, can have plural, but not clashing, sets of attributes; I saw it. Here + now was Acts. But also (this is terribly, terribly vital!) also USA 1974. Acts AD 45 did not replace USA 1974; it was not here instead. This is impossible. But if it can be done with USA 1974 it can be done -can be so- with any set of space-time accidents. Any century + any place. + I have what the AI voice said: "He causes things to look different". Not
